               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Wǝddāse ʾAmlāk “Praise of God” (fols. 2ra-123rb)
 I-1) Monday’s
                     prayer of Basil of Caesarea (fols. 2ra-16ra)
 I-2) Tuesday’s prayer of
                     Efrem the Syrian (fols. 16rb-39vb)
 I-3) Wednesday’s prayer of Efrem the
                     Syrian (fols. 39vb-57ra)
 I-4) Thursday’s prayer of John Saba (ʾAragāwi
                     Manfasawi) (fols. 57rb-78va)
 I-5) Friday’s prayer of Shenute (78va-88ra)
                     and Pachomius (fols. 88ra-96rb)
 I-6) Saturday’s prayer of Athanasius of
                     Alexandria (fols. 96rb-109rb)
 I-7) Sunday’s prayer of Cyril of Alexandria
                     (fols. 109rb-123rb)
 II) ʾArgānona wǝddāse “The Harp of Praise” (fols.
                     124ra-233rb)
 II-1) Monday (fols. 124ra-143ra)
 II-2) Tuesday (fols.
                     144ra-161vb)
 II-3) Wednesday (fols. 162ra-179va)
 II-4) Thursday
                     (fols. 180ra-198rb)
 II-5) Friday (fols. 198rb-214va)
 II-6) Saturday
                     (fols. 214vb-223va)
 II-7) Sunday (fols. 223vb-233rb)
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
